summary: DURING MY PLASMA DONATION AT CSL PLASMA A PROBLEMIST ENCOURAGED ME TO GET A SCOOTER THIS SCOOTER WAS/IS A 150CC SCOOTER. NOW, I AM A DISABLE INDIVIDUAL USING PUBLIC TRANSPORTATION, AND IT'S ALONG BUS ROUTES THAT GAVE ME TROUBLE OUT OF TOWN.
